---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Dr. Soheyl Simaei — Founder"
  description="Dr. Soheyl Simaei is a veterinarian, entrepreneur, and educator. Founder of Academia Europa and Veterinary Academy International (VAI)."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Founder"
    title="Dr. Soheyl Simaei."
    lede="Founder & Chief Executive Officer, Academia Europa. Founder, Veterinary Academy International."
  />

  <Section>
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Dr. Soheyl Simaei is a veterinarian, entrepreneur, and educator. He is the founder of Academia Europa and of Veterinary Academy International (VAI), its first specialised academy.</p>
      <p>Before founding Academia Europa, Dr. Simaei spent more than two decades in veterinary practice, clinical leadership, and veterinary entrepreneurship, building and leading a respected veterinary business in Dubai. This experience now informs his work in postgraduate veterinary education, professional development, and clinical leadership training.</p>
      <p>His work today focuses on building educational systems that help experienced professionals progress from competence to mastery, leadership, and meaningful professional contribution.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Educational Vision" title="The question behind Academia Europa." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Dr. Simaei founded Academia Europa to address a question he has spent years observing in practice: <em>why does professional education so rarely produce the practitioners it promises?</em></p>
      <p>His answer — and the foundation of Academia Europa — is structure: deliberate pathways, documented standards, expert faculty, and learning that translates into real clinical and professional behaviour.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Roles">
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-graphite text-lg max-w-3xl">
      <li class="flex gap-4 items-baseline"><span class="text-champagne text-xs tracking-[0.2em]">—</span> Founder & Chief Executive Officer, Academia Europa</li>
      <li class="flex gap-4 items-baseline"><span class="text-champagne text-xs tracking-[0.2em]">—</span> Founder, Veterinary Academy International (VAI)</li>
      <li class="flex gap-4 items-baseline"><span class="text-champagne text-xs tracking-[0.2em]">—</span> Founder, Veterinary Longevity</li>
    </ul>
  </Section>
</Base>
